29 Aug 2024 20:13:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/israels-taekwondo-athlete-asaf-yasur-takes-gold-medal-in-paris-2024-paralympics/00000191-9fa3-d0ae-af93-ffff75260000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方称哈马斯伪造加沙战争民意调查结果以夸大公众支持率</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-says-hamas-falsified-gaza-war-poll-results-to-exaggerate-public-support/00000191-9f6a-d794-a7f5-dffb5ce90000</link><description>以色列国防军声称，它发现了一些文件，揭示了哈马斯如何操纵受人尊敬的巴勒斯坦民意调查来抬高哈马斯的支持率。民意调查专家哈利勒·希卡基 (Khalil Shikaki) 回应道：“这听起来像是[以色列]军队和哈马斯之间为了塑造公众舆论而进行的一场叙事战争”</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 19:21:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-says-hamas-falsified-gaza-war-poll-results-to-exaggerate-public-support/00000191-9f6a-d794-a7f5-dffb5ce90000</guid></item><item><title>世卫组织官员称以色列军方同意加沙人道主义暂停以进行脊髓灰质炎疫苗接种</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/who-official-says-israeli-military-agrees-to-gaza-humanitarian-pauses-for-polio-shots/00000191-9f36-d0ae-af93-ffff9d430000</link><description>以色列军方支持短暂停火，但正在等待政府做出决定，允许在加沙出现首例小儿麻痹症后为 60 万名儿童接种疫苗</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 18:33:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/who-official-says-israeli-military-agrees-to-gaza-humanitarian-pauses-for-polio-shots/00000191-9f36-d0ae-af93-ffff9d430000</guid></item><item><title>帮助和教唆犹太定居者的恐怖活动：现在会产生真正的后果吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-29/ty-article/.highlight/aiding-and-abetting-jewish-settler-terror-will-there-now-be-real-consequences/00000191-9ecc-d453-ab9f-feccc2f20000</link><description>以色列军队高层承认定居者的暴力行为，并称其为恐怖主义行为。现在，它必须对允许和教唆这些犯罪的士兵实施与对平民相同的处罚</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 18:30:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">ht