/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-said-public-pool-was-closed-opened-it-for-ultra-orthodox-with-gender-segregation/00000191-9eb3-d453-ab9f-febf91990000</link><description>本月，一个市政游泳池在性别隔离的情况下悄然运营了几天，通过市政府的托拉文化部门提供打折门票，而市政府则隐瞒了该项目预算的详细信息</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 16:00:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-said-public-pool-was-closed-opened-it-for-ultra-orthodox-with-gender-segregation/00000191-9eb3-d453-ab9f-febf91990000</guid></item><item><title>“我希望有人付钱给我，我会和他住在一起，每个星期天我都会为他写弥撒。就是这样&amp;#39;</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-08-29/ty-article/.highlight/i-want-someone-to-pay-me-ill-live-with-him-and-every-sunday-ill-write-a-mass-for-him/00000191-9ea1-d172-abd9-feb73a470000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一名年轻的以色列妇女与她的父亲一起飞往哥本哈根以获得外国公民身份，另一名妇女准备与她的双胞胎妹妹一起从军</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 15:33:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-08-29/ty-article/.highlight/i-want-someone-to-pay-me-ill-live-with-him-and-every-sunday-ill-write-a-mass-for-him/00000191-9ea1-d172-abd9-feb73a470000</guid></item><item><title>新报告称，到 2023 年，纽约 44% 的仇恨犯罪都是以犹太人为目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/jews-were-target-of-44-percent-of-all-hate-crimes-in-new-york-in-2023-says-new-report/00000191-9e37-d18a-a1b7-bf378fed0000</link><description>纽约州审计长的一份新报告显示，纽约市所有重罪仇恨犯罪中有 65% 是针对犹太人的，而且越来越多的攻击针对的是人而不是财产</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 14:32:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/jews-were-target-of-44-percent-of-all-hate-crimes-in-new-york-in-2023-says-new-report/00000191-9e37-d18a-a1b7-bf378fed0000</guid></item><item><title>英国航空和伊比利亚快运周五恢复往返以色列的航班</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/british-airways-iberia-express-resume-flights-to-from-israel-on-frida